<div class="content-box">
    <h2>The Post-Framework World</h2>
    <p>
        In an ideal world, frameworks still exist, but they become thin layers of opinionated "sugar" on top of powerful native APIs. Switching from a React component to an Angular component should be as easy as toggling an option, because underneath, they maximize the use of the same shared <strong>Web Everything</strong> protocols.
    </p>

